{"results":[{"aya":"057","id":1859,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"他说：使者们啊！你们有什么差事呢？","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"058","id":1860,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"他们说：我们奉派去惩治一群犯罪的民众。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"059","id":1861,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"鲁特的家族除外，我们确要把他们全都救出来；","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"060","id":1862,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"但他的妻子除外，我们已预定她和其余的人同受刑罚。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"061","id":1863,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"当使者们来到鲁特的家里的时候，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"062","id":1864,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"他说：你们确是一些陌生的人。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"063","id":1865,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"他们说：不然；我们把他们一向争论的（刑罚）带来给你了。","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":15,"previousPage":"/zh/s015-8.json","nextPage":"/zh/s015-10.json"}}